OL,3,CMet chief warns British Jews facing
OL,4,Cgreatest threat after Golders Green
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FBritish Jews are facing their greatest
OL,8,Fever threat, the head of the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police has warned in the
OL,10,Fwake of the Golders Green stabbing.
OL,12,FSir Mark Rowley said that Jews were
OL,13,Ffacing a "ghastly Venn diagram" of
OL,14,Fhate from all sides, and warned
OL,15,Fantisemitism was a growing threat to
OL,16,Ftheir safety because of social media,
OL,17,Fin an interview with the Times.
OL,26,@uD@JOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
