PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777701895
OL,3,CMet chief warns British Jews facing
OL,4,Cgreatest threat after Golders Green
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FThe Met Commissioner's warning comes
OL,8,Fjust two days after a stabbing at
OL,9,FGolders Green, in which two Jewish men
OL,10,Fwere injured.
OL,12,FIt is the latest in a number of
OL,13,Fincidents where the Jewish community
OL,14,Fhas been targeted.
OL,16,FSpeaking to the Times, Sir Mark said:
OL,17,F"Every racist or extremist or
OL,18,Fterrorist group has a list of people
OL,19,Fthey hate because they all create an
OL,20,F'other' who they want to blame
OL,21,Feverything on and visit everything on.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777701895
OL,3,CMet chief warns British Jews facing
OL,4,Cgreatest threat after Golders Green
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,F"The ghastly fact is that Jews are on
OL,8,Feverybody's list, all of those hateful
OL,9,Fgroups, whether you're extreme right,
OL,10,Fwhether you're extreme left, whether
OL,11,Fyou're Islamist terrorist, whether
OL,12,Fyou're right-wing terrorist, and some
OL,13,Fhostile states as well now with some
OL,14,Fsort of Iranian-related threats.
OL,15,FThere's a ghastly Venn diagram that
OL,16,Fthey're at the middle of."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777701895
OL,3,CMet chief warns British Jews facing
OL,4,Cgreatest threat after Golders Green
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FThe "social media-led" news ecosystem
OL,8,Fwhich has developed online means more
OL,9,Fpeople are getting their views from
OL,10,F"non-traditional sources", Sir Mark
OL,11,Fsaid, adding that antisemitism was
OL,12,F"becoming more and more mainstreamed".
OL,14,FThe Met Commissioner also revealed he
OL,15,Fhas requested urgent funding to
OL,16,Frecruit 300 officers to protect the
OL,17,FJewish community, with plans for a
OL,18,Fdedicated group of police to patrol
OL,19,Fnorth west London.
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@VO]rD@AOUrD@YO]tD@AOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
