OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777701895
OL,3,CMet chief warns British Jews facing
OL,4,Cgreatest threat after Golders Green
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FSir Mark also defended the two
OL,8,Fofficers who detained the suspect in
OL,9,Fthe Golders Green attack.
OL,11,FIn footage shared on social media, the
OL,12,Fofficers appeared to kick the 45-year-
OL,13,Fold suspect in the head after they had
OL,14,Fused a Taser to force him to the
OL,15,Fground.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
