SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777701895
OL,3,CMet chief warns British Jews facing
OL,4,Cgreatest threat after Golders Green
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister also branded Mr
OL,8,FPolanski "disgraceful" and "not fit to
OL,9,Flead any political party" for
OL,10,Freposting the criticism of police
OL,11,Fofficers.
OL,13,FThe Green leader has apologised for
OL,14,F"sharing a tweet in haste".
OL,16,FBut Mr Polanski then hit back, saying
OL,17,Fin response to a clip of the Prime
OL,18,FMinister's interview: "Yesterday in
OL,19,FHastings, in the wake of antisemitic
OL,20,Fattacks in Golders Green, I faced Nazi
OL,21,Fsalutes.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@VO]pD@\OUqD@YO]vD@AOUvD@ZO]zD@
OL,26,AWOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777701895
OL,3,CMet chief warns British Jews facing
OL,4,Cgreatest threat after Golders Green
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,F"Today the Prime Minister uses his
OL,8,Foffice to attack the only Jewish party
OL,9,Fleader to score political points."
OL,11,FMr Polanski is expected to meet Sir
OL,12,FMark following the local elections on
OL,13,FMay 7, to discuss matters related to
OL,14,Fhis apology, the Met confirmed.
OL,16,FEarlier, the Director of Public
OL,17,FProsecutions warned of a "deeply
OL,18,Ftroubling rise" in antisemitic
OL,19,Fincidents across the country, as he
OL,20,Fvowed to use the "full force of the
OL,21,Flaw" against perpetrators.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@bO]yD@ZOUzD@OO]|D@ROU}D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
