OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777701895
OL,3,CMet chief warns British Jews facing
OL,4,Cgreatest threat after Golders Green
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FThe UK terrorism threat level was
OL,8,Fraised to "severe" by the Joint
OL,9,FTerrorism Analysis Centre, meaning a
OL,10,Fterror attack is "highly likely",
OL,11,Ffollowing the Golders Green attack.
OL,13,FSuspect Essa Suleiman appeared in
OL,14,Fcourt on Friday charged with thee
OL,15,Fcounts of attempted murder, including
OL,16,Fof his own friend before allegedly
OL,17,Fstabbing two Jewish men, Shloime Rand,
OL,18,F34, and Norman Shine, 76.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@RO]rD@ROUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777701895
OL,3,CMet chief warns British Jews facing
OL,4,Cgreatest threat after Golders Green
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FSuleiman, who was born in Somalia and
OL,8,Fcame to the UK legally as a child in
OL,9,Fthe 1990s, was remanded in custody
OL,10,Funtil the next hearing at the Old
OL,11,FBailey on May 15.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
